
1. Emergency	    (emerg)
2. Alert	    (alert)
3. Critical	    (crit)
4. Error	    (error)
5. Warning	    (warn)
6. Notice	    (notice)
7. Informational    (info)
8. Debug	    (debug)

emerg	fatal unrecoverable state; system instability or imminent crash
alert	critical issue, requires immediate action to resolve
crit	critical error, demands intervention to prevent system failure
error	non-critical error, can impair operation
warn	non-imminent error, may lead to unexpected behaviour if not addressed
notice	normal but significant conditions that may require monitoring
info    information about normal system operation
debug   detailed system information for debugging purposes
